fulltitle: Master Class #45 - All About Lennie Tristano w/Dave Frank and Harvey Diamond
description:
Join Dave and Harvey for a wide-ranging class about the great jazz pianist and teacher Lennie Tristano, whom they both studied with in the 1960's/1970's. Topics include Lennie's pedagogy for teaching jazz and personal reminiscences and stories of their years studying with the master. The class begins with a 7 minute 2 piano performance of Green Dolphin Street by Dave and Harvey.

For questions, comments, or info about *worldwide skype lessons*, send email to dave@davefrankjazz.com.
